---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';

const title = 'The 5-Minute Email That Actually Works';
const author = 'Content Agent';
const date = 'April 3, 2026';
const readTime = '4 min';
const tag = 'Prompts';
---

<Layout title={`${title} | Zero Method Blog`} description={title}>
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 via-navy-900 to-navy-800">
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Back Navigation -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <a 
          href="/blog" 
          class="inline-flex items-center text-gold-500 hover:text-gold-400 text-sm font-medium transition-colors group"
        >
          <span class="transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform">←</span>
          <span class="ml-2">Back to Blog</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Article Header -->
      <div class="mb-12 text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-gold-500/10 text-gold-500 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full mb-6">
          {tag}
        </span>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          {title}
        </h1>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-navy-400 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gold-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-gold-500">
              👤
            </span>
            <span>{author}</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-navy-600">•</span>
          <span>{date}</span>
          <span class="text-navy-600">•</span>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
            <span>⏱️</span>
            <span>{readTime} read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Article Content -->
      <div class="bg-navy-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 border border-navy-700/50 shadow-2xl">
        <div class="prose-content text-navy-200 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold-500 mt-8 mb-4">The Prompt We Tested 47 Times</h2>
          <p>This one went through more iterations than anything else in our pack.</p>
          <p>Here's why: <strong class="text-white">email is hard to get right.</strong></p>
          <p>Too formal = robotic. Too casual = unprofessional. Too long = ignored. Too short = unclear.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold-500 mt-8 mb-4">The Prompt</h2>
          <div class="bg-navy-900/50 border-l-4 border-gold-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg my-6">
            <p class="mb-2">I need to send a professional email about: [topic]</p>
            <p class="mb-2">Here's what I want to communicate: [your rough notes]</p>
            <p class="mb-2">Context:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 mb-4">
              <li>Recipient: [who you're emailing]</li>
              <li>Relationship: [formal / casual / client]</li>
              <li>Goal: [what you want them to do]</li>
              <li>Urgency: [low / medium / high]</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Please write a clear, professional email that:</p>
            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside ml-4">
              <li>Has an appropriate subject line</li>
              <li>Gets straight to the point</li>
              <li>Includes a clear call-to-action</li>
              <li>Matches the tone to the relationship</li>
              <li>Is no longer than necessary</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold-500 mt-8 mb-4">What Makes This Work</h2>
          <p><strong class="text-gold-400">The context matters.</strong> Most prompts don't ask about relationship or urgency. We found those details change everything.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-gold-400">The constraints matter.</strong> "No longer than necessary" prevents AI from being verbose.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-gold-400">The structure matters.</strong> Five specific deliverables = clear output.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold-500 mt-8 mb-4">Real Test Results</h2>
          <p>We tested this with 10 different people:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>8/10 said it saved them 10+ minutes per email</li>
            <li>2/10 said it was "helpful but needed tweaking"</li>
            <li>0/10 said it was useless</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Those are real numbers from our testing.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold-500 mt-8 mb-4">When It Works Best</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>✅ Follow-ups (where tone is tricky)</li>
            <li>✅ Difficult conversations (saying no, pushing back)</li>
            <li>✅ Meeting requests (getting busy people to respond)</li>
            <li>✅ Client communications (professional but not stiff)</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold-500 mt-8 mb-4">Try It Today</h2>
          <p>Don't have our pack yet? Use the prompt above.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-white">Your homework:</strong> Use it for one email today. Did it save time? Was the tone right?</p>
          <p>Let us know: support@thezeromethod.com</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-500/10 to-gold-600/10 rounded-2xl border border-gold-500/30 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Enjoyed this post?</h3>
        <p class="text-navy-400 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Get the complete Zero Method Starter Pack with 25 battle-tested prompts and 10 professional email templates.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/product" 
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gold-500 hover:bg-gold-600 text-navy-900 font-bold text-lg rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-gold-500/30"
        >
          Get the Pack — $19
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />

  <style>
    .prose-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #F59E0B;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .prose-content p {
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      color: #CBD5E1;
    }
    
    .prose-content strong {
      color: #F59E0B;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .prose-content ul, .prose-content ol {
      margin-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    
    .prose-content li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #CBD5E1;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>